Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Decision Risk Module Stub
Provides comprehensive risk assessment with VaR, CVaR, portfolio optimization, and stress testing
Enables Monte Carlo simulation, uncertainty modeling, and dynamic risk monitoring
:End Note

Type RiskMeasure is Dictionary with:
    measure_id as String
    measure_type as String
    measure_value as Float
    confidence_level as Float
    time_horizon as Float
    measure_metadata as Dictionary

Type Asset is Dictionary with:
    asset_id as String
    asset_name as String
    asset_type as String
    asset_returns as List[Float]
    asset_volatility as Float
    asset_correlation as Dictionary
    asset_metadata as Dictionary

Type PortfolioRisk is Dictionary with:
    portfolio_id as String
    assets as List[Asset]
    weights as List[Float]
    portfolio_return as Float
    portfolio_volatility as Float
    portfolio_var as Float
    portfolio_cvar as Float
    risk_decomposition as Dictionary[String, Float]
    portfolio_metadata as Dictionary

Type StressScenario is Dictionary with:
    scenario_id as String
    scenario_name as String
    scenario_type as String
    scenario_parameters as Dictionary
    scenario_probability as Float
    scenario_impact as Dictionary
    scenario_metadata as Dictionary

Type UncertaintyModel is Dictionary with:
    model_id as String
    model_type as String
    uncertain_variables as List[UncertainVariable]
    correlation_structure as Matrix
    distribution_parameters as Dictionary
    model_metadata as Dictionary

Type UncertainVariable is Dictionary with:
    variable_id as String
    variable_name as String
    variable_type as String
    distribution_type as String
    distribution_parameters as Dictionary
    variable_bounds as List[Float]
    variable_metadata as Dictionary

Type RiskProfile is Dictionary with:
    profile_id as String
    risk_tolerance as Float
    risk_preferences as Dictionary
    risk_constraints as List[Dictionary]
    risk_metadata as Dictionary

Type RiskMonitor is Dictionary with:
    monitor_id as String
    monitoring_frequency as String
    risk_thresholds as Dictionary
    alert_mechanisms as List[String]
    monitoring_metadata as Dictionary

Type RiskManagementSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    risk_models as List[RiskModel]
    risk_monitors as List[RiskMonitor]
    risk_analyzers as List[RiskAnalyzer]
    system_configuration as Dictionary
    system_metadata as Dictionary

Process called "calculate_var" that takes returns as List[Float] and confidence_level as Float and method as String returns RiskMeasure
Process called "calculate_historical_var" that takes returns as List[Float] and confidence_level as Float returns Float
Process called "calculate_parametric_var" that takes returns as List[Float] and confidence_level as Float returns Float
Process called "calculate_monte_carlo_var" that takes returns as List[Float] and confidence_level as Float returns Float
Process called "calculate_cvar" that takes returns as List[Float] and confidence_level as Float returns RiskMeasure
Process called "create_portfolio_risk" that takes assets as List[Asset] and weights as List[Float] and returns_data as Dictionary returns PortfolioRisk
Process called "calculate_portfolio_variance" that takes weights as List[Float] and covariance_matrix as Matrix returns Float
Process called "calculate_risk_decomposition" that takes assets as List[Asset] and weights as List[Float] and covariance_matrix as Matrix returns Dictionary[String, Float]
Process called "create_stress_scenario" that takes config as Dictionary returns StressScenario
Process called "run_stress_test" that takes portfolio_risk as PortfolioRisk and stress_scenarios as List[StressScenario] returns Dictionary
Process called "run_monte_carlo_risk_simulation" that takes portfolio_risk as PortfolioRisk and simulation_config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_uncertainty_model" that takes config as Dictionary returns UncertaintyModel
Process called "propagate_uncertainty" that takes uncertainty_model as UncertaintyModel and function_model as Dictionary and num_samples as Integer returns Dictionary
Process called "make_risk_adjusted_decision" that takes alternatives as List[Dictionary] and risk_profile as RiskProfile and uncertainty_model as UncertaintyModel returns Dictionary
Process called "calculate_risk_adjusted_score" that takes expected_return as Float and risk_measures as Dictionary and risk_tolerance as Float returns Float
Process called "create_dynamic_risk_monitor" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "update_risk_monitoring" that takes monitor as Dictionary and current_portfolio as PortfolioRisk and market_data as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_risk_management_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_risk_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 